      <title>美国在一名美国人死亡几天后公布对哈马斯的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/us-unseals-charges-against-hamas-days-after-death-of-american</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部周二宣布，已指控哈马斯六名高级领导人犯有恐怖主义罪和密谋杀害美国人罪。几天前，包括一名以色列裔美国人在内的六名人质在加沙地带被杀害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/us-unseals-charges-against-hamas-days-after-death-of-american</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 22:09:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的 Starlink 项目放弃，誓言阻止巴西的 X 项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/musk-s-starlink-backs-down-vows-to-comply-and-block-x-in-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克的卫星互联网提供商 Starlink 改变了方针，表示将遵守巴西最高法院的命令，阻止拉丁美洲最大的国家访问这位亿万富翁的社交网络 X。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/musk-s-starlink-backs-down-vows-to-comply-and-block-x-in-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:33:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普未能将纽约封口费案移交联邦法院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/trump-loses-bid-to-move-ny-hush-money-case-to-federal-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名美国法官裁定，前总统唐纳德·特朗普不能在定于 9 月 18 日宣判之前将其纽约封口费案转交给联邦法院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/trump-loses-bid-to-move-ny-hush-money-case-to-federal-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:15:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部誓言不会在选举前对 Meta 和 X 施加压力，以打击外国干预</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/us-vows-no-pre-election-pressure-on-meta-x-to-fight-foreign-meddling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有指控称社交媒体平台此前受到胁迫后，当政府分享有关外国对国家安全或选举构成威胁的信息时，美国司法部不会向社交媒体公司施压，要求其删除或屏蔽内容。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/us-vows-no-pre-election-pressure-on-meta-x-to-fight-foreign-meddling</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:05:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在美国移民法庭，正义并不是重点。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-03/tribunales-inmigracion-eeuu-en-manos-de-politica-y-le-falla-a-solicitantes-asilo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[决定庇护案件的系统正在失败，不仅仅是因为它不堪重负。必须采取一些重大措施来修复存在根本缺陷的流程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-03/tribunales-inmigracion-eeuu-en-manos-de-politica-y-le-falla-a-solicitantes-asilo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:03:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 在不断升级的反垄断调查中收到美国司法部传票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/nvidia-gets-doj-subpoena-in-escalating-antitrust-investigation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部向英伟达公司和其他公司发出传票，寻找该芯片制造商违反反垄断法的证据，这是其对这家人工智能处理器主要供应商的调查升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/nvidia-gets-doj-subpoena-in-escalating-antitrust-investigation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 20:24:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛预计特朗普胜选将打击美国 GDP，民主党获胜将提振美国 GDP</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/goldman-sees-us-gdp-hit-from-trump-win-boost-if-democrats-sweep</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团经济学家对共和党或民主党在 11 月大选中获胜可能带来的经济影响进行了分析，并警告说，如果唐纳德·特朗普获胜，美国 GDP 将面临打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/goldman-sees-us-gdp-hit-from-trump-win-boost-if-democrats-sweep</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 19:17:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登自冻结许可以来首次批准新的液化天然气项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/biden-grants-first-new-lng-approval-since-freezing-permits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自联邦法院推翻暂停发放液化天然气运输许可证的命令以来，拜登政府颁发了首张液化天然气出口许可证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/biden-grants-first-new-lng-approval-since-freezing-permits</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 17:39:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约州州长前助理霍楚尔被指控为中国外国代理人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/ex-top-aide-to-ny-governor-is-arrested-on-foreign-agent-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曾任纽约州州长凯西·霍楚尔和安德鲁·库莫高级助理的琳达·孙因被联邦指控担任中国未注册的外国代理人，以换取数百万美元而被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/ex-top-aide-to-ny-governor-is-arrested-on-foreign-agent-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:38:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国比亚迪暂停墨西哥工厂建设计划直至美国大选结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/china-s-byd-said-to-pause-mexico-plant-until-after-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，中国最大的电动汽车制造商比亚迪股份有限公司至少要在美国大选之后才会宣布在墨西哥投资大型工厂，因为美国政策的变化迫使全球企业进入观望模式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/china-s-byd-said-to-pause-mexico-plant-until-after-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:14:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
